oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Miss Fannie Rhea Frith
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Portrait of Miss Fannie Rhea Frith posing in summer gown. See also #1545. She was friends with Kate Ransom (#4110, #28295).

Fannie Rhea Frith (1884-?) was the daughter of James Hinton Frith (1858-1927) & Fannie Wilson Frith (1862-1946). Her mother filed for divorce in the Davidson Co. Chancery Court in 1907. She married Samuel M. Williams in 1904.
